[[File:Cardio_Regulator_belt.jpg|thumb|right|Cardio-regulator belt]]
The '''cardio-regulator''' was a belt designed to enhance the fortitude of its wearer. It actively monitored [[Heart/Legends|heartbeat]] and breathing, and should either of them become irregular, it would release chemicals into the body to stabilize.

==Appearances==
*''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]'' {{1st}}
